    </div>
    <div class="pvh-faq-grid" data-pvh-enter>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>Will my cat actually use it? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Most cats approach Brook within the first few hours. Running water triggers their natural investigation instinct. Some take a day or two. If yours is the rare exception after a fair trial, our 30-day guarantee covers you completely — no return needed.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>How loud is the pump? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Under 25 decibels — quieter than a household fridge. Most owners forget it's running until they hear their cat drinking from it.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>How long does delivery take? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">EU orders typically arrive in 7–14 business days. You'll receive a tracking number by email once your order ships. If it hasn't arrived within 20 business days, contact us and we'll sort it immediately.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>Is it dishwasher safe? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Yes. Every part disassembles and goes on the top rack. Because it's ceramic, nothing warps or holds bacteria the way plastic fountains do after repeated washing.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>How often do I replace the filter? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Once a month with regular use. The triple-stage filter saturates after about 30 days. We recommend marking the date when you first set it up.</div>
      </details>
      <details class="pvh-faq-item">
        <summary>What's in the box? <span class="pvh-faq-chevron" aria-hidden="true">+</span></summary>
        <div class="pvh-faq-answer">Brook ceramic fountain bowl and base, silent circulation pump, 1× triple-stage filter cartridge, EU power adapter (or rechargeable battery unit, depending on model), and a setup guide. Everything you need, nothing you don't.</div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

